This is the suite of unit and integration tests for the Crop and Stitch nodes.

In order to run these tests:
- Copy the content of testimgs/ to ComfyUI input/.
- Enable DEBUG_MODE in inpaint_cropandstitch.py
- Reload this workflow and run.

You can find the end-to-end tests (using both crop and stitch) below this note.
